'''約瑟夫·巴拉特·柯內爾'''（'''{{lang|en|Joseph Bharat Cornell}}'''，{{bd|19xx|catIdx=C康奈爾，約瑟夫 B.}}）是[[美國|美國]]的自然教育家。他在1970年代後期所撰寫的著作《與孩子分享自然》，積極提倡{{le|戶外學習|Outdoor education}}，對當時的教育引起很大的震撼。直到現在的20多年，這本書在全世界被翻譯成15種語言，總銷量超過50萬冊<ref name = "dawnpub">
{{cite web |url=http://www.dawnpub.com/our-authorsillustrators/joseph-cornell/ |title=Joseph Cornell |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date= |website=dawnpub.com |publisher=Dawn Publications |accessdate=8 August 2013}}
</ref><ref name = "campmag2011">
{{cite web |url=http://www.acacamps.org/campmag/1109/creating-community-nature-interview-joseph-cornell |title=Creating Community through Nature - An Interview With Joseph Cornell |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date= September 2011 |website=acacamps.org |publisher=American Camping Association |accessdate=8 August 2013}}</ref>。

他在1979年成立分享自然基金會（Sharing Nature Foundation），用以資助自然教育活動。

==著作列表==
* Sharing Nature With Children Book'' 系列
*# "Sharing Nature With Children: the classic parents' and teachers' nature awareness guidebook", (1984，1998年再版), Dawn Publications, CA: USA. ISBN 1883220734
*# "Sharing the Joy of Nature: Nature Activities for All Ages", (1989，1998年再版), Dawn Publications, Nevada City, CA: USA. ISBN 0916124525
*# "John Muir: My Life With Nature", (2000), Dawn Publications, CA: USA. ISBN 0606256482 (硬皮本) / ISBN 1584690097 (平裝本)
* Sharing Nature Pocket Guide
*# "With Beauty Before Me: An Inspirational Guide for Nature Walks", (2000), Dawn Publications, CA: USA. ISBN 1584690127
* "Listening to Nature: How to Deepen Your Awareness of Nature", (1987), Dawn Publications, Nevada City, CA: USA. ISBN 0916124355
* "Journey to the Heart of Nature: A Guided Exploration", (1995), Dawn Publications, Nevada City, CA: USA. ISBN 1883220068
* "Ocean Animals Clue Game", (1995), Dawn Publications, Nevada City, CA: USA. ISBN 1883220270
* "Rainforest Animals Clue Game", (1995), Dawn Publications, Nevada City, CA: USA. ISBN 1883220440

